A complete C grammar.
Author:
Robert Grimm
Version:
$Revision: 1.20 $
module xtc.lang.C;

define TranslationUnit = 
  ExternalDeclaration* Annotations
  ;

define ExternalDeclaration = 
  Declaration { yyValue = ... }
  / FunctionDefinition { yyValue = ... }
  / AssemblyDefinition { yyValue = ... }
  / EmptyDefinition { yyValue = ... }
  ;

define FunctionDefinition = 
  ("__extension__":Keyword)? DeclarationSpecifiers? Declarator 
  DeclarationList? CompoundStatement
  ;

define DeclarationList = 
  DeclarationListEntry+
  ;

expand DeclarationListEntry = 
  Declaration
  ;

define EmptyDefinition = /* Empty */ ;

define Annotations = 
  { yyValue = ... }
  ;

define Declaration = 
  ("__extension__":Keyword)? DeclarationSpecifiers InitializedDeclaratorList?
  ;

define DeclarationSpecifiers = 
  DeclarationSpecifierPlus
  ;

define> DeclarationSpecifierPlus = 
  DeclarationSpecifier+
  ;

expand DeclarationSpecifier = 
  StorageClassSpecifier
  / TypeSpecifier
  / TypeQualifier
  / FunctionSpecifier
  / AttributeSpecifier
  ;

define InitializedDeclaratorList = 
  InitializedDeclarator InitializedDeclarator*
  ;

define InitializedDeclarator = 
  AttributeSpecifierList? Declarator SimpleAssemblyExpression? 
  AttributeSpecifierList? Initializer?
  ;

expand StorageClassSpecifier = 
  AutoSpecifier
  / ExternSpecifier
  / RegisterSpecifier
  / StaticSpecifier
  / ThreadSpecifier
  / TypedefSpecifier
  ;

define AutoSpecifier = /* Empty */ ;

define ExternSpecifier = /* Empty */ ;

define RegisterSpecifier = /* Empty */ ;

define StaticSpecifier = /* Empty */ ;

define ThreadSpecifier = /* Empty */ ;

define TypedefSpecifier = /* Empty */ ;

expand TypeQualifier = 
  VolatileQualifier
  / ConstantQualifier
  / RestrictQualifier
  ;

define VolatileQualifier = 
  "volatile":Keyword
  / "__volatile":Keyword
  / "__volatile__":Keyword
  ;

define ConstantQualifier = 
  "const":Keyword
  / "__const":Keyword
  / "__const__":Keyword
  ;

define RestrictQualifier = 
  "restrict":Keyword
  / "__restrict":Keyword
  / "__restrict__":Keyword
  ;

define FunctionSpecifier = 
  "inline":Keyword
  / "__inline":Keyword
  / "__inline__":Keyword
  ;

expand TypeSpecifier = 
  EnumerationTypeSpecifier
  / StructureTypeSpecifier
  / UnionTypeSpecifier
  / FloatingPointTypeSpecifier
  / IntegerTypeSpecifier
  / TypedefName
  / TypeofSpecifier
  / VoidTypeSpecifier
  / VarArgListSpecifier
  ;

expand EnumerationTypeSpecifier = 
  EnumerationTypeDefinition
  / EnumerationTypeReference
  ;

define EnumerationTypeDefinition = 
  AttributeSpecifierList? Identifier? EnumeratorList AttributeSpecifierList?
  ;

define EnumeratorList = 
  Enumerator Enumerator*
  ;

define Enumerator = 
  Identifier ConditionalExpression?
  ;

define EnumerationTypeReference = 
  AttributeSpecifierList? Identifier
  ;

expand StructureTypeSpecifier = 
  StructureTypeDefinition
  / StructureTypeReference
  ;

define StructureTypeDefinition = 
  AttributeSpecifierList? Identifier? StructureDeclarationList 
  AttributeSpecifierList?
  ;

define StructureTypeReference = 
  AttributeSpecifierList? Identifier
  ;

expand UnionTypeSpecifier = 
  UnionTypeDefinition
  / UnionTypeReference
  ;

define UnionTypeDefinition = 
  AttributeSpecifierList? Identifier? StructureDeclarationList 
  AttributeSpecifierList?
  ;

define UnionTypeReference = 
  AttributeSpecifierList? Identifier
  ;

define StructureDeclarationList = 
  AnnotatedStructureDeclaration+ Annotations
  / Annotations
  ;

define AnnotatedStructureDeclaration = 
  StructureDeclaration { yyValue = ... }
  ;

define StructureDeclaration = 
  ("__extension__":Keyword)? SpecifierQualifierList 
  OptionalStructureDeclaratorList
  ;

define SpecifierQualifierList = 
  SpecifierQualifierPlus
  ;

define> SpecifierQualifierPlus = 
  SpecifierQualifier+
  ;

expand SpecifierQualifier = 
  TypeSpecifier
  / TypeQualifier
  / AttributeSpecifier
  ;

expand OptionalStructureDeclaratorList = 
  StructureDeclaratorList
  / null
  ;

define StructureDeclaratorList = 
  StructureDeclarator StructureDeclarator*
  ;

expand StructureDeclarator = 
  BitField
  / AttributedDeclarator
  ;

define BitField = 
  AttributeSpecifierList? Declarator? ConditionalExpression 
  AttributeSpecifierList?
  ;

define AttributedDeclarator = 
  AttributeSpecifierList? Declarator AttributeSpecifierList?
  ;

expand Declarator = 
  PointerDeclarator
  / DirectDeclarator
  ;

define PointerDeclarator = 
  Pointer DirectDeclarator
  ;

define Pointer = 
  TypeQualifierList Pointer?
  ;

define TypeQualifierList = 
  TypeQualifierList$$Choice1*
  ;

expand TypeQualifierList$$Choice1 = 
  TypeQualifier
  / AttributeSpecifier
  ;

define DirectDeclarator = 
  DirectDeclarator ( /* Choice */ 
    ParameterTypeList @FunctionDeclarator
    / IdentifierList? @FunctionDeclarator
    / ArrayQualifierList ( /* Choice */ 
      AssignmentExpression? @ArrayDeclarator
      / VariableLength @ArrayDeclarator
    )
  )
  / yyValue:AttributedDeclarator
  / yyValue:SimpleDeclarator
  ;

define VariableLength = /* Empty */ ;

define SimpleDeclarator = 
  Identifier
  ;

define ParameterTypeList = 
  ParameterList ("...":Symbol)?
  ;

define ParameterList = 
  ParameterDeclaration ParameterDeclaration*
  ;

define ParameterDeclaration = 
  DeclarationSpecifiers ( /* Choice */ 
    Declarator AttributeSpecifierList?
    / AbstractDeclarator? AttributeSpecifierList?
  )
  ;

define AttributedAbstractDeclarator = 
  AttributeSpecifierList? AbstractDeclarator
  ;

define AbstractDeclarator = 
  Pointer? DirectAbstractDeclarator
  ;

define DirectAbstractDeclarator = 
  DirectAbstractDeclarator ( /* Choice */ 
    "[":Symbol ( /* Choice */ 
      AssignmentExpression?
      / VariableLength
    )
    / "(":Symbol ParameterTypeList?
  )
  / yyValue:AttributedAbstractDeclarator
  / yyValue:null
  ;

define IdentifierList = 
  Identifier Identifier*
  ;

define ArrayQualifierList = 
  ArrayQualifierList$$Choice1*
  ;

expand ArrayQualifierList$$Choice1 = 
  ArrayQualifier
  / AttributeSpecifier
  ;

expand ArrayQualifier = 
  StaticSpecifier
  / VolatileQualifier
  / RestrictQualifier
  / ConstantQualifier
  ;

expand FloatingPointTypeSpecifier = 
  Complex
  / Double
  / Float
  ;

define Complex = 
  "_Complex":Keyword
  / "__complex__":Keyword
  ;

define Double = /* Empty */ ;

define Float = /* Empty */ ;

expand IntegerTypeSpecifier = 
  Long
  / Int
  / Short
  / Char
  / Bool
  / Unsigned
  / Signed
  ;

define Long = /* Empty */ ;

define Int = /* Empty */ ;

define Short = /* Empty */ ;

define Char = /* Empty */ ;

define Bool = /* Empty */ ;

define Unsigned = /* Empty */ ;

define Signed = 
  "signed":Keyword
  / "__signed":Keyword
  / "__signed__":Keyword
  ;

define TypedefName = 
  Identifier
  ;

define TypeofSpecifier = 
  TypeName
  / CommaExpression
  ;

define VoidTypeSpecifier = /* Empty */ ;

define VarArgListSpecifier = /* Empty */ ;

expand Initializer = 
  InitializerList
  / AssignmentExpression
  ;

define InitializerList = 
  InitializerListEntry InitializerListEntry*
  / 
  ;

define InitializerListEntry = 
  Designation? Initializer
  ;

define Designation = 
  Designator+
  / yyValue:ObsoleteArrayDesignation
  / yyValue:ObsoleteFieldDesignation
  ;

define Designator = 
  "[":Symbol ConditionalExpression
  / "[":Symbol ConditionalExpression ConditionalExpression
  / ".":Symbol PrimaryIdentifier
  ;

define ObsoleteArrayDesignation = 
  "[":Symbol ConditionalExpression ( /* Choice */ 
    
    / ConditionalExpression
  )
  ;

define ObsoleteFieldDesignation = 
  Identifier
  ;

define TypeName = 
  SpecifierQualifierList AbstractDeclarator?
  ;

define AttributeSpecifierList = 
  AttributeSpecifierPlus
  ;

define> AttributeSpecifierPlus = 
  AttributeSpecifier+
  ;

define AttributeSpecifier = 
  AttributeList?
  ;

define AttributeList = 
  AttributeListEntry AttributeListEntry*
  ;

define AttributeListEntry = 
  Word ExpressionList?
  ;

expand Statement = 
  ExpressionStatement
  / CompoundStatement
  / ConditionalStatement
  / IterationStatement
  / SwitchStatement
  / LabeledStatement
  / BreakStatement
  / ContinueStatement
  / ReturnStatement
  / GotoStatement
  / AssemblyStatement
  / EmptyStatement
  ;

define LabeledStatement = 
  Label Statement
  / Label null
  ;

expand Label = 
  NamedLabel
  / CaseLabel
  / DefaultLabel
  ;

define NamedLabel = 
  Identifier AttributeSpecifierList?
  ;

define DefaultLabel = /* Empty */ ;

define CaseLabel = 
  ConditionalExpression ConditionalExpression
  / ConditionalExpression
  ;

define CompoundStatement = 
  LocalLabelDeclarationStar DeclarationOrStatementStar Annotations
  ;

define> LocalLabelDeclarationStar = 
  LocalLabelDeclaration*
  ;

define LocalLabelDeclaration = 
  Identifier Identifier*
  ;

define> DeclarationOrStatementStar = 
  DeclarationOrStatement*
  ;

define DeclarationOrStatement = 
  Declaration { yyValue = ... }
  / Statement { yyValue = ... }
  ;

expand ConditionalStatement = 
  IfElseStatement
  / IfStatement
  ;

define IfElseStatement = 
  CommaExpression Statement Statement
  ;

define IfStatement = 
  CommaExpression Statement
  ;

expand IterationStatement = 
  WhileStatement
  / DoStatement
  / ForStatement
  ;

define WhileStatement = 
  CommaExpression Statement
  ;

define DoStatement = 
  Statement CommaExpression
  ;

define ForStatement = 
  InitialClause CommaExpression? CommaExpression? Statement
  ;

expand InitialClause = 
  Declaration
  / CommaExpression?
  ;

define SwitchStatement = 
  CommaExpression Statement
  ;

define BreakStatement = /* Empty */ ;

define ContinueStatement = /* Empty */ ;

define ReturnStatement = 
  CommaExpression?
  ;

define GotoStatement = 
  null PrimaryIdentifier
  / "*":Symbol CommaExpression
  ;

define ExpressionStatement = 
  CommaExpression
  ;

define EmptyStatement = /* Empty */ ;

define CommaExpression = 
  CommaExpression AssignmentExpression
  / yyValue:AssignmentExpression
  ;

define AssignmentExpression = 
  UnaryExpression AssignmentOperator AssignmentExpression
  / yyValue:ConditionalExpression
  ;

expand AssignmentOperator = 
  "=":Symbol
  / "+=":Symbol
  / "-=":Symbol
  / "*=":Symbol
  / "/=":Symbol
  / "%=":Symbol
  / "<<=":Symbol
  / ">>=":Symbol
  / "&=":Symbol
  / "^=":Symbol
  / "|=":Symbol
  ;

define ConditionalExpression = 
  LogicalOrExpression CommaExpression ConditionalExpression
  / LogicalOrExpression null ConditionalExpression
  / yyValue:LogicalOrExpression
  ;

define LogicalOrExpression = 
  LogicalOrExpression LogicalAndExpression
  / yyValue:LogicalAndExpression
  ;

define LogicalAndExpression = 
  LogicalAndExpression BitwiseOrExpression
  / yyValue:BitwiseOrExpression
  ;

define BitwiseOrExpression = 
  BitwiseOrExpression BitwiseXorExpression
  / yyValue:BitwiseXorExpression
  ;

define BitwiseXorExpression = 
  BitwiseXorExpression BitwiseAndExpression
  / yyValue:BitwiseAndExpression
  ;

define BitwiseAndExpression = 
  BitwiseAndExpression EqualityExpression
  / yyValue:EqualityExpression
  ;

define EqualityExpression = 
  EqualityExpression EqualityOperator RelationalExpression
  / yyValue:RelationalExpression
  ;

expand EqualityOperator = 
  "==":Symbol
  / "!=":Symbol
  ;

define RelationalExpression = 
  RelationalExpression RelationalOperator ShiftExpression
  / yyValue:ShiftExpression
  ;

expand RelationalOperator = 
  "<=":Symbol
  / "<":Symbol
  / ">=":Symbol
  / ">":Symbol
  ;

define ShiftExpression = 
  ShiftExpression ShiftOperator AdditiveExpression
  / yyValue:AdditiveExpression
  ;

expand ShiftOperator = 
  "<<":Symbol
  / ">>":Symbol
  ;

define AdditiveExpression = 
  AdditiveExpression AdditiveOperator MultiplicativeExpression
  / yyValue:MultiplicativeExpression
  ;

expand AdditiveOperator = 
  "+":Symbol
  / "-":Symbol
  ;

define MultiplicativeExpression = 
  MultiplicativeExpression MultiplicativeOperator CastExpression
  / yyValue:CastExpression
  ;

expand MultiplicativeOperator = 
  "*":Symbol
  / "/":Symbol
  / "%":Symbol
  ;

define CastExpression = 
  TypeName CastExpression
  / yyValue:UnaryExpression
  ;

expand UnaryExpression = 
  SizeofExpression
  / AlignofExpression
  / OffsetofExpression
  / TypeCompatibilityExpression
  / UnaryMinusExpression
  / UnaryPlusExpression
  / LogicalNegationExpression
  / BitwiseNegationExpression
  / AddressExpression
  / LabelAddressExpression
  / IndirectionExpression
  / PreincrementExpression
  / PredecrementExpression
  / ExtensionExpression
  / PostfixExpression
  ;

define SizeofExpression = 
  TypeName !"{":Symbol
  / UnaryExpression
  ;

define AlignofExpression = 
  TypeName !"{":Symbol
  / UnaryExpression
  ;

define OffsetofExpression = 
  TypeName PostfixExpression
  ;

define TypeCompatibilityExpression = 
  TypeName TypeName
  ;

define UnaryMinusExpression = 
  CastExpression
  ;

define UnaryPlusExpression = 
  CastExpression
  ;

define LogicalNegationExpression = 
  CastExpression
  ;

define BitwiseNegationExpression = 
  CastExpression
  ;

define AddressExpression = 
  CastExpression
  ;

define IndirectionExpression = 
  CastExpression
  ;

define PreincrementExpression = 
  UnaryExpression
  ;

define PredecrementExpression = 
  UnaryExpression
  ;

define LabelAddressExpression = 
  Identifier
  ;

define ExtensionExpression = 
  CastExpression
  ;

define PostfixExpression = 
  PostfixExpression ( /* Choice */ 
    CommaExpression @SubscriptExpression
    / Identifier @DirectComponentSelection
    / Identifier @IndirectComponentSelection
    / ExpressionList? @FunctionCall
    / @PostincrementExpression
    / @PostdecrementExpression
  )
  / yyValue:CompoundLiteral
  / yyValue:PrimaryExpression
  ;

define ExpressionList = 
  AssignmentExpression AssignmentExpression*
  ;

define CompoundLiteral = 
  TypeName InitializerList
  ;

expand PrimaryExpression = 
  Constant
  / PrimaryIdentifier
  / StatementAsExpression
  / VariableArgumentAccess
  / CommaExpression
  ;

define PrimaryIdentifier = 
  Identifier
  ;

define StatementAsExpression = 
  CompoundStatement
  ;

define VariableArgumentAccess = 
  AssignmentExpression TypeName
  ;

define AssemblyDefinition = 
  SimpleAssemblyExpression
  ;

define SimpleAssemblyExpression = 
  StringConstant
  ;

define AssemblyStatement = 
  TypeQualifier? AssemblyArgument ";":Symbol
  ;

define AssemblyArgument = 
  StringConstant ( /* Choice */ 
    AssemblyOperands? ( /* Choice */ 
      AssemblyOperands? ( /* Choice */ 
        AssemblyClobbers
        / 
      )
      / 
    )
    / 
  )
  ;

define AssemblyOperands = 
  AssemblyOperand AssemblyOperand*
  ;

define AssemblyOperand = 
  Word? StringConstant CommaExpression
  ;

define AssemblyClobbers = 
  StringConstant StringConstant*
  ;

expand Constant = 
  FloatingConstant
  / IntegerConstant
  / CharacterConstant
  / StringConstant
  ;

define IntegerConstant = 
  HexConstant
  / OctalConstant
  / DecimalConstant
  ;

define DecimalConstant = ... ;

define HexConstant = ... ;

define OctalConstant = ... ;

define FloatingConstant = 
  DecimalFloatingConstant
  / HexFloatingConstant
  ;

define DecimalFloatingConstant = ... ;

define HexFloatingConstant = ... ;

define CharacterConstant = 
  WideCharacterLiteral
  / CharacterLiteral
  ;

define WideCharacterLiteral = ... ;

define CharacterLiteral = ... ;

define StringConstant = 
  StringConstant$$Choice1+
  ;

expand StringConstant$$Choice1 = 
  WideStringLiteral
  / StringLiteral
  ;

define WideStringLiteral = ... ;

define StringLiteral = ... ;

expand Identifier = 
  Word
  ;

expand Keyword = 
  Word
  ;

expand Word = 
  WordCharacters
  ;

define WordCharacters = ... ;

expand Symbol = 
  SymbolCharacters
  ;

define SymbolCharacters = ... ;
